{"id":1258,"date":"2021-07-14T10:00:00","date_gmt":"2021-07-14T08:00:00","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?p=1258"},"modified":"2021-10-14T09:21:15","modified_gmt":"2021-10-14T07:21:15","slug":"fireside-chat-with-suzanne-dumouchel","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/2021\/07\/fireside-chat-with-suzanne-dumouchel\/","title":{"rendered":"Fireside Chat with Suzanne Dumouchel"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<p>In this fireside chat with Suzanne Dumouchel, TRIPLE Project &amp; Scientific Coordinator, SSHOC Partner and a Member of the Board of Directors of the <a href=\"https:\/\/eosc.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">EOSC Association<\/a>, we ask her about the complementarities between SSHOC and TRIPLE services and the value they will bring to <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/eosc-portal.eu\/enhance\" target=\"_blank\">EOSC Enhance<\/a> and <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/www.dariah.eu\/activities\/projects-and-affiliations\/eosc-future\/\" target=\"_blank\">EOSC Future<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed alignwide is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<div  style=\"display: block; margin: 0px auto;\"  id=\"_ytid_27075\" class=\"__youtube_prefs__  __youtube_prefs_gdpr__  epyt-is-override \" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy=\"1\" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=\"\"><p><strong>Please accept YouTube cookies to play this video.<\/strong> By accepting you will be accessing content from YouTube, a service provided by an external third party.<\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/policies.google.com\/privacy\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">YouTube privacy policy<\/a><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/privacy-policy\/\">TRIPLE privacy policy<\/a><\/p>\n<p>If you accept this notice, your choice will be saved and the page will refresh.<\/p>\n<button type=\"button\" class=\"__youtube_prefs_gdpr__\">Accept YouTube Content<img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/plugins\/youtube-embed-plus\/images\/icon-check.png\" alt=\"accept\" data-no-lazy=\"1\" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=\"\" \/><\/button><\/div>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">SSHOC <\/a>provides a comprehensive research environment for researchers in the Social Sciences and the Humanities (SSH). Its <a href=\"https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/ssh-open-marketplace\">SSH marketplace<\/a> is a user-centric service for collaboration and knowledge sharing across SSH communities. Its value stems from the automatic ingestion and updating of SSH resources such as <strong>tools <\/strong>and <strong>trainings <\/strong>from third parties (thus suggesting improvements of scientific workflows for the SSH researchers); continuous curation of the information by the marketplace\u2019s editorial team and contributions from its users, the SSH community.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TRIPLE is working in complementarity with the SSHOC project. With the multilingual discovery platform <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/gotriple-platform\/\">GOTRIPLE<\/a>, TRIPLE provides a single access point that allows you to explore, find, access and reuse materials such as <strong>research publications and data<\/strong>, <strong>projects <\/strong>and <strong>researcher profiles<\/strong> at European scale.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Both projects work in concert on service governance to optimise user involvement and improve SSH research. As thematic hubs, SSHOC and TRIPLE will bring to the European Open Science Cloud (<a href=\"https:\/\/ec.europa.eu\/info\/research-and-innovation\/strategy\/goals-research-and-innovation-policy\/open-science\/european-open-science-cloud-eosc_en\">EOSC<\/a>): research tools and training materials, publications and data as well as other SSH resources, enabling researchers to increase the value of their SSH research and to facilitate innovation. The services from both projects will help build bridges with other scientific communities with a view to boosting interdisciplinarity and contributions to societal challenges.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>SSHOC and TRIPLE bring to the European Open Science Cloud a rich and diverse pool of stakeholders, as illustrated in the image below.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/op.europa.eu\/en\/publication-detail\/-\/publication\/af7f7807-6ce1-11eb-aeb5-01aa75ed71a1\/language-en\/format-PDF\/source-190694287\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"751\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/framework_actors_eosc_ecosystem_skills-1024x751.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1262\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/framework_actors_eosc_ecosystem_skills-1024x751.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/framework_actors_eosc_ecosystem_skills-300x220.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/framework_actors_eosc_ecosystem_skills-768x563.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/07\/framework_actors_eosc_ecosystem_skills.png 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Framework of actors in the EOSC ecosystem (source: <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https:\/\/op.europa.eu\/en\/publication-detail\/-\/publication\/af7f7807-6ce1-11eb-aeb5-01aa75ed71a1\/language-en\/format-PDF\/source-190694287\" target=\"_blank\">Digital skills for FAIR and Open Science. Report from the EOSC Executive Board Skills and Training Working Group, p. 17<\/a>)<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div style=\"height:30px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Watch the Fireside Chat video<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/youtu.be\/Tk6jD17zlrs\">https:\/\/youtu.be\/Tk6jD17zlrs<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Find out more about TRIPLE<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Find out more about SSHOC<\/strong>: <a href=\"https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/\">https:\/\/sshopencloud.eu\/<\/a> <\/p>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator has-text-color has-background has-black-background-color has-black-color\"\/>\n\n\n\n<p>This article has also been published on the SSHOC website: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.sshopencloud.eu\/news\/fireside-chat-suzanne-dumouchel\">Fireside Chat with Suzanne Dumouchel | SSHOPENCLOUD<\/a>.<\/p>\n<\/div>","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In this fireside chat with Suzanne Dumouchel, TRIPLE Project &amp; Scientific Coordinator, SSHOC Partner and a Member of the Board of Directors of the EOSC Association, we ask her about the complementarities between SSHOC and TRIPLE services and the value<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":1259,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[23,11],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1258"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1258"}],"version-his